Project Scope

 What the System Will Do
•	The system will let students create and submit weekly activity logs online.
•	The system will let workplace supervisors review, approve or return those logs with written comments.
•	The system will let academic supervisors score students using set criteria and have the system compute the final score automatically.
•	Let the administrator manage user accounts, assign internship placements, define scoring criteria, and view reports.
•	Enforce submission deadlines so late submissions are automatically blocked.
•	Keep a full history of every action taken on each log so nothing is lost.

What the System Will NOT Do
	The system will not manage payments or financial records related to internships.
	It will not send SMS or email notifications (this may be added later).
	It will not handle company registration or job postings.
	It will not connect to any existing Makerere University system at this stage.


